"{\"uid\": \"newseu.cgtn.com-news-2024-04-12-Prize-money-for-athletes-to-polarize-Olympics--1sIRn383DXi-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Louise Greenwood  Copied  Olympic gold, silver and bronze medals in a Louis Vuitton trunk, which will transport and protect them during the Paris 2024 Olympic and Paralympic Games.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 205, \"end\": 211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princess_Louise_of_Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9995455317005226, \"rank\": 0.0004433498237589547, \"text\": \"Louise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princess_Louise_of_Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princess_Louise_of_Belgium\"}, {\"begin\": 212, \"end\": 221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Humphry_Greenwood\", \"score\": 0.996200996419003, \"rank\": 0.0017804047733398676, \"text\": \"Greenwood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Humphry_Greenwood\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Humphry_Greenwood\"}, {\"begin\": 275, \"end\": 288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.9379650183803365e-12, \"text\": \"Louis Vuitton\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\"}, {\"begin\": 368, \"end\": 384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999874635251, \"rank\": 1.077261767794747e-08, \"text\": \"Paralympic Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/Stephanie Lecocq/Reuters  Plans to pay prize money to athletes taking part in the Olympic Games this summer, risks \\\"polarizing\\\" the games, according to one sports historian.\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Philip Barker, editor of the Journal of Olympic History, told CGTN Europe that the plans put the tradition of the 'gentleman amateur' among competitors at risk.\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 722, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"World Athletics, the international athletics federation, says it will pay Olympic gold medal winners $50,000 at the Paris games in July.\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 724, \"end\": 739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.618325073856815e-14, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}, {\"begin\": 840, \"end\": 845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999663487, \"rank\": 3.3722209563724075e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletics governing body is putting aside a budget of $2.4m to reward winners across 48 events at the track and field programme.\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Plans are also underway to pay silver and bronze medallists at the 2028 Olympics in Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1090, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1078, \"end\": 1089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999176907, \"rank\": 6.686390793308392e-11, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Its President Sebastian Coe has admitted it is \\\"a pivotal moment\\\" for the Olympic movement but not at odds with the spirit of the games.\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1106, \"end\": 1119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Coe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sebastian Coe\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Coe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Coe\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The beneficiaries of growth are the sports and ultimately the athlete,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think this sits firmly behind those principles and philosophies that they espouse as well.\\\"\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1405, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports historian Phillip Barker disagrees vehemently.\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1460, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1424, \"end\": 1438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phillip_Barker_(film_director)\", \"score\": 0.9999963453745684, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phillip Barker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phillip_Barker_(film_director)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phillip_Barker_(film_director)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He told CGTN Europe: \\\"It's something that's going to polarize the Olympic world, not because the Olympics are amateur anymore, as they once were, but because the positioning of the Olympic Games is always that they are so much more than just a sporting event.\\\"\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1721, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Describing a \\\"pecking order\\\" for Olympic sports, he predicted that the largest payments will be awarded to those taking part in track, gymnastics and aquatics events.\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1889, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE  Botswana offers to send Germany 20,000 elephants  Genetic clues to left-handedness revealed  European pasta market beats to Turkish durum  Swedish pole vaulter Armand Duplantis calls the change \\\"a good thing\\\"/ Reuters  Barker points out that this is not the first time financial incentives have been used at the games  \\\"In fact, in 1993, in Stuttgart .. because Mercedes was sponsoring the championship and each winner got a car that was valued at around $28,000.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  However, describing regulations written when the modern games began in 1896, he adds the Olympic authorities \\\"set great store by being a gentleman amateur\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 There were people who were actually excluded from the Olympics because if they \\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 played professionally as a cricketer, they could not compete as a footballer.\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 2688, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1926, \"end\": 1933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.9995693308217254, \"rank\": 0.00025571589936858693, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}, {\"begin\": 2026, \"end\": 2033, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_language\", \"score\": 0.8956224256904023, \"rank\": 0.11056434396905346, \"text\": \"Turkish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2041, \"end\": 2048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"score\": 0.9999880639569018, \"rank\": 1.0268985360823832e-05, \"text\": \"Swedish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\"}, {\"begin\": 2062, \"end\": 2078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Armand Duplantis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\"}, {\"begin\": 2112, \"end\": 2119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999999912697604, \"rank\": 8.717125062793897e-09, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 2243, \"end\": 2252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuttgart\", \"score\": 0.9999999495494206, \"rank\": 4.8813269680813714e-08, \"text\": \"Stuttgart\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuttgart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuttgart\"}, {\"begin\": 2264, \"end\": 2272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mercedes-Benz\", \"score\": 0.9091761407806466, \"rank\": 0.09893075603767526, \"text\": \"Mercedes\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mercedes-Benz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mercedes-Benz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So (it was) much, much stricter in those days.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Defending the change, the International Olympic Committee insists that the bulk of its budgets still go to promoting sport around the world.\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2880, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2766, \"end\": 2797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This means that, every day, the equivalent of $4.2 million goes to help athletes and sports organisations at all levels around the world,\\\" it said.\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 3029, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The reaction from competitors \\u00a0has been mixed.\", \"from\": 3031, \"to\": 3077, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Swedish pole vaulter Armand Duplantis,\\u00a0who plans to take part in the Paris games called it \\\"a good thing \\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 considering at the last Olympics there was no prize money at all.\\\"\", \"from\": 3078, \"to\": 3253, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3078, \"end\": 3085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"score\": 0.9999880639569018, \"rank\": 1.0268985360823832e-05, \"text\": \"Swedish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\"}, {\"begin\": 3099, \"end\": 3115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Armand Duplantis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\"}, {\"begin\": 3147, \"end\": 3152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999663487, \"rank\": 3.3722209563724075e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Norwegian Hurdler Karsten Warholm agreed, saying: \\\"To me it does not change my motivation to win because, for the Olympics I am not in it for the money.\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3407, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3255, \"end\": 3264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.9997722213291859, \"rank\": 0.00022505573981816224, \"text\": \"Norwegian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}, {\"begin\": 3273, \"end\": 3288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karsten_Warholm\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Karsten Warholm\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karsten_Warholm\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karsten_Warholm\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But when it comes to building a professional sport, I think it's going in the right direction.\\\"\", \"from\": 3408, \"to\": 3503, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe toStoryboard: A weekly newsletterbringing you the best of CGTN every Friday  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 3505, \"to\": 3852, \"entities\": []}]}"